snippet.title: To The Core Trailer (release date August 10)
snippet.description:
Wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1988550/To_The_Core/

join to the core community server: https://discord.gg/mEzQkfRRJj

To The Core is an incremental game about drilling and using the resources from the orbiting planets to buy upgrades to drill even further and deeper than before!

The planned release date is August 10th!
